      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and fading paint on the hood, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, but it may require some upcoming maintenance for minor fluid leaks and suspension bushings. It is a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
