    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts reliably and delivers smooth, consistent power, making it a dependable choice for daily driving or longer trips. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal use, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and mechanically sound. Buyers can expect a road-ready vehicle that offers a comfortable ride and has plenty of life left in it.",
