    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 in concours-level condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains factory-tight with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed VANOS system for peak variable valve timing precision. Suspension geometry is optimized via Bilstein PSS10 adjustable dampers, while the rear end utilizes a perfectly shimmed limited-slip differential. Every panel retains its original factory depth, and the undercarriage is free of any fluid seepage or oxidation. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
