    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, finished in a timeless coat that glows under any light. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear or creasing, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, showcasing a meticulously maintained powerplant that has been serviced exclusively by certified specialists with a full, documented history. The undercarriage is equally pristine, reflecting a life spent in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather. This is more than just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for someone who demands perfection in every detail.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
